<msbt attribsize="4">
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />好，<delay8 />我们到了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />本次的目的地就是这个岛！
</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="1" />，
我想您是第一次参加这个旅行，
所以请让我简单说明一下<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak />在这个岛上找到的材料和生物
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />都可以自由地带回家！<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><pageBreak />如果忘了带道具，<delay8 />或是道具损坏了，
也可以通过里数兑换来解决哦。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不过，
有一点务必要注意<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak />如果回去的时候把东西忘在岛上了，<delay20 />
那就无法再取回了<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak />所以请慎重管理随身物品，
不要把重要的东西放在地上<delay20 />
忘记带走哦！<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="0" />好了<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要说明的<delay8 />就是这么多了！</message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />我会在这里待命，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />想要回去或是需要道具时，<delay8 />
请随时跟我说哦！<pageBreak /><anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />祝你好运！</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="04 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你好！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />请问有什么需要呢？</message>
	<message label="002_a" attrib="00 00 00 00">我想回去</message>
	<message label="002_b" attrib="00 00 00 00">我想要道具</message>
	<message label="002_c" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Negative" target="player" targetSpec="" />没什么事</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="02 00 00 00">要结束在这里的探险，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />返回<tag a="110" b="34" />吗？</message>
	<message label="003_a" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="player" targetSpec="" />是的</message>
	<message label="003_b" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Negative" target="player" targetSpec="" />等一下</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 00"><snpcAnim id="DodRoger" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />收到！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那么，<delay8 />出发吧！</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明白了！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有需要的时候，<delay20 />请再跟我说。</message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />需要工具吗？<delay40 />
可以在这里用里数兑换！</message>
	<message label="012" attrib="00 00 00 00">需要工具吗？<10_4 />
不好意思，因为持有物已满，<delay20 />
请整理好包包再来找我吧！</message>
	<message label="013" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哎呀，<delay8 />不用了吗？<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有需要的时候，<delay20 />请再跟我说。</message>
	<message label="014" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />兑换<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><delay8 />
需要<tag a="90" b="40" arg="0xcd00" />，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />您的里数好像不够呢<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />等累积到足够的里数后，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />请一定要来兑换！</message>
	<message label="015" attrib="02 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />兑换<tag a="125" b="0" arg="0x0" /><delay8 />
需要<tag a="90" b="40" arg="0xcd00" />，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要兑换吗？</message>
	<message label="015_a" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="player" targetSpec="" />要兑换！</message>
	<message label="015_b" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Negative" target="player" targetSpec="" />还是算了</message>
	<message label="016" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />非常感谢！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那么，请收下这个！</message>
	<message label="017" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是还有其他需要，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />请尽管跟我说吧！</message>
	<message label="021" attrib="00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />哦！意识恢复了吗！！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />别再让人这么担心了！<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />这座岛上好像还有危险的虫子，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以请千万要小心！<pageBreak /><size value="75" /><tag a="10" b="12" /><snpcAnim id="DodWireless" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay frames="50" />我是机长陆德里，<delay20 />确认客户平安无事！<delay frames="30" />
紧急异常状态取消！　<delay frames="30" />完毕<delay frames="90" />
<100_3 arg="PlaneAnnounceOn" /><delay20 /><colour id="5" />（收到！<delay20 />请继续多多关照！）<delay20 /><100_3 arg="PlaneAnnounceOff" /><colour id="65535" /><10_7 arg="30" />
<size value="100" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那么，请重新打起精神<tag a="110" b="0" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />祝你好运！</message>
